dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the district boundaries in Uganda for 2006. These are the level 5 administrative (ADM5) boundaries. These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
